{"tid":1881063,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IG多次遭入侵　IU警告黑客：唔好再越界！","createTime":"2020-02-15T09:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T12:53:04.000Z","uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"58e9d434b4402e69a716105a69a2b5c6421a1e9b","tid":1881063,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:43:14.000Z","msg":"韓國靚聲女歌手IU不時透過Instagram（IG）跟粉絲分享近況，上月就曾公開多張與家人去海外旅行的照片，而她今日在IG Story透露有黑客入侵她的IG帳號，令她感到困擾：「我都沒有進入IG，但就關注了不認識的帳號。」<br />\n<br />\nIU指她收到了不少短訊，提醒她IG帳號的密碼疑被黑客試圖破解，連她早前在拍攝韓劇《德魯爾酒店》時開設的「張滿月」帳號也同樣曾被黑客入侵，IU又警告黑客停止入侵帳號的行為：「不要再這樣做，這是我擁有的東西，越過這條界線就是侵犯了，Beep！」<br />\n<br />\n而IU最近為玄彬與孫藝珍主演劇集《愛的迫降》演唱主題曲《I Give You My Heart》，完整版本將於香港時間今午5點公開，IU亦不忘在IG Story提醒大家留意新歌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200215/photo/bkn-20200215164010401-0215_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200215164743\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200215%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200215164010401-0215_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200215164743&h=b3e90c42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cd6d9f691be543d6da568bd825341c1a5d5bcdb","tid":1881063,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/52ad9bf1c8671769d2280ff74bd39c14/2c96427a3153c657-76/s400x600/0d061a0364f3e163c6a3972c2eddc6757d152b67.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F52ad9bf1c8671769d2280ff74bd39c14%2F2c96427a3153c657-76%2Fs400x600%2F0d061a0364f3e163c6a3972c2eddc6757d152b67.gif&h=9485e80d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪再搞我女友"},{"pid":"4d44e8b4d1d8e8841474677dc717ee874aafed61","tid":1881063,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2b93203990c9b8da392e8c83b8a6a4c2ac3057","tid":1881063,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"